{
  "stem": "13198.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I always-- always went in for charring.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because that was rather basic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you got tips for charring, if you charred properly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They would tip you with a bit of food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, you'd get an extra bit of milk or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] so somehow or other, I managed to survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was what was so marvelous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That-- we were there with top of the everything-- of brilliant professors.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the Jews are pretty good at organizing themselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They organized that there would be lectures, and that professors would give lectures in their specialities.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you couldn't just go there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You had to apply for seats.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to everything I could get hold of because I--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was in the evening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- we were told there'd be a lecturer there and there, somewhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you saw that you organized yourself to be-- to be able to go there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went and listened to-- we got away from the world and into a world of what we were used to.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
